Depends: R(>= 3.5.0)
Description: R port of the replication files for "Evaluating Monetary Policy 
    Counterfactuals: (When) Do We Need Structural Models?" by Caravello, 
    McKay and Wolf. Implements Bayesian VAR estimation, impulse response 
    analysis, and frequency domain variance decomposition using Armadillo 
    for efficient matrix computations.
